"And that's the man whom you have been eating your heart out over?" Doc nodded towards the door. "You may consider him a man, I would say he was a mentally adolescent cad." "Oh, Doc..." Gay protested weakly, "you don't know Gavin." "I've only met him today but I think I can safely say that I know him a great deal better than you do."
